{
 "name": "RPlog_Vornskr_Attack",
 "title": "Vornskr Attack: A Beast in the Myrkr Woods",
 "summary": "On a misty morning in the woods outside Karrde's base on Myrkr, the Jedi Jessalyn and her companion Simon walk a forest path, both robbed of their Force connection by the planet's vornskr-spawned bubbles, when a desperate cry rings out. They rush in--joined by Drew, Toby, and other operatives--to find the mechanic Orson cornered against a tree by a large, hungry vornskr, fending it off with only a twig. Without the Force to guide them, Jessalyn and Simon fight clumsily but bravely: Simon pole-vaults into the beast with his staff, Toby snaps off a covering blaster shot, and Drew drags the bleeding Orson clear. As the cornered, vornskr lashes out with its poison-barbed tail at Simon, Jessalyn severs it with a desperate lightsaber stroke; howling and maimed, the creature finally bolts back into the forest. The shaken survivors regroup around the wounded Orson, Simon checking on Jessalyn before turning to the obvious question of whether the ship captain is all right.",
 "rows": [
